{"tid":1848503,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇斯克查：山神今夏強勢回歸","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T13:36:18.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec28cf4bec627237f0f559e7e8c3297977d3768a","tid":1848503,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:20:17.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】曼聯領隊蘇斯克查表示，阿歷斯山齊士將會由意大利外借回歸，並在曼聯取得成功。<br />\n<br />\n31歲的阿歷斯山齊士（Alexis Sanchez）於今季被外借至意甲國際米蘭，蘇斯克查確認他將會在今個夏天回歸：「山齊士會在夏天回來證明你們錯了。」<br />\n<br />\n自2018年1月由阿仙奴加盟曼聯後，山齊士為球隊上陣45場只攻入5球，而且他更在曼聯領着40萬鎊的周薪，表現一直被受批評。就算外借至國米，山神亦受傷患困擾，今季只為國米上陣過7場及攻入1球。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，蘇斯克查亦指一月增兵有難度。「我們有球員正在努力恢復，這是一個非常困難的轉會窗，一直都是這樣，有些球會不想失去他們最好的球員，我已記不起有多少個好球員在1月引入，拿臣是好球員、維迪和艾夫拿都是很好的收購。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"cba10afbce5caf4c75f8ed75af0e02bafb5e5da4","tid":1848503,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/98e5fcb3a7e63bb4a3dc745ae16a850d/tumblr_pyjw2oTHKK1t6sag7o2_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F98e5fcb3a7e63bb4a3dc745ae16a850d%2Ftumblr_pyjw2oTHKK1t6sag7o2_500.gif&h=db8d12bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/3a7c061dccd3dbf8683debcfb4a2999b/tumblr_pyjw2oTHKK1t6sag7o1_500.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F3a7c061dccd3dbf8683debcfb4a2999b%2Ftumblr_pyjw2oTHKK1t6sag7o1_500.gifv&h=9ed822f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d91ce8e5d52fcd406ee065417951ed874e5b86","tid":1848503,"uid":138762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:31:57.000Z","msg":"擺明國米唔想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830384ccab74d4f36c54f49769b9536f1d9946eb","tid":1848503,"uid":15660,"like":0,"di